{"tid":1707912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［BBQ？唔割］燒左咪燒左囉，重要得過警車撞人同中槍？","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:18:50.000Z","uid":87790,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"188348f04d2ae18f33d4ef88e0adaffa51de172d","tid":1707912,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"喂，燒左咪燒左囉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亂世之中無d手段同畫面嚇下d 藍色綠色物件,等佢地下次斬人無咁事無忌憚，佢斬人個時唔通摺紙鶴摺死佢咩？<br />\n<br />\n你行街見到個黑社會 攞把老牛望住，係人都行快兩步啦下話，咁佢咁做咪少左人攻擊佢囉。<br />\n<br />\n燒完少左嚇到對家，少左自己人受傷，大家諗下係好事定壞事。"},{"pid":"f00160b82653a8e3779df4f27c86ede21c00befc","tid":1707912,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a761a5bd290e94a3965e10460c0aa52697b86086","tid":1707912,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:10:11.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"c7530406c63130b0c6593ba50f4ae017a26384da","tid":1707912,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d147e83331abb41656656a55b4a0adb16eb45bf9","tid":1707912,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:14:02.000Z","msg":"各位手足，而家亂世呀，和平時代個個有事就用法律姐，而家唔好講法律公唔公平，你唔還拖，法律保護你之前都可能比人斬死左啦。"},{"pid":"9c7db51c9acd13142b6e733945c7d0e6a287c648","tid":1707912,"uid":208505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割，何況BBQ?"},{"pid":"85fb1af5cb13e3287aff0ac8d933c557cde0b52b","tid":1707912,"uid":87790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c7db51c9acd13142b6e733945c7d0e6a287c648","tid":1707912,"uid":208505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割，何況BBQ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"講得好"},{"pid":"45d732f37324d18cd9134c966d66c40e966ee931","tid":1707912,"uid":87790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:21: